shows.overview: A pair of horny college guys get summer jobs at a sexy cheerleader camp.

shows.title: #DigitalLivesMatter
shows.overview: Hijinks ensue, when a disgruntled fan of a social media superstar hacks into his Instagram account and removes the star's millions of followers.

shows.title: #IMomSoHard Live
shows.overview: A two-woman show about friendship, periods, sex after marriage, body image, and parenting failures from comics Kristin Hensley and Jen Smedley.

shows.title: #Jowable
shows.overview: Elsa is a troubled young woman who is yearning for a mature and intimate relationship. AUDIO IN TAGALOG

shows.title: #LoveSwag
shows.overview: Bronson, a legendary-mogul, is able to bed women at will. That was until he developed an embarrassing medical condition that renders his mastery in the bedroom which is unacceptable with the ladies. On his way to getting his swagger back, restoring his name, and redeeming his company's respectability, will he have to run-out on the only woman eager to stay by his side and nurse him back to health?

shows.title: #LuckyNumber
shows.overview: A man on a losing streak jumps to VIP and A-List status when he gets the old cell number of his basketball idol, who is about to find out the ruse.

shows.title: #Roxy
shows.overview: When a girl falls for a hunky quarterback, her shy, but brainy friend conspires with the athlete to create a dream boy and woo her via social media.

shows.title: Selfie
shows.overview: Two days before their final exams, three teen girls make a seaside getaway to have the time of their lives.

shows.title: #Stuck
shows.overview: A hot one-night stand turns into an awkward morning after when GUY and HOLLY get STUCK in a dead-stopped traffic jam. As they begrudgingly get to know each other, we learn of their sexually raucous evening and then they're led to their surprising destiny.

shows.title: #FriendButMarried
shows.overview: Pining for his high school crush for years, a young man puts up his best efforts to move out of the friend zone until she reveals she's getting married.

shows.title: #FriendButMarried 2
shows.overview: As Ayu and Ditto finally transition from best friends to newlyweds, a quick pregnancy creates uncertainty for the future of their young marriage.

shows.title: #Xmas
shows.overview: When interior designer, Jen, is selected for a social media competition for a design brand, she poses as an influencer with her best friend playing her husband and her nephew as her baby. Stars Clare Bowen and Brant Daugherty.

shows.title: #realityhigh
shows.overview: Dani basks in the attention after she befriends Alexa, the meanest and hottest girl at the school. Soon, her college aspirations start to falter as she delves into the cool-kid world.
Joe enlists the help of a friendly woman as he sets out to fleece the criminally over-privileged of one-million dollars from a safe-deposit vault.

shows.title: $5 a Day
shows.overview: Christopher Walken is hilarious as Nat, an eccentric con-artist and deadbeat dad dying to reconnect with his troubled son, Flynn (Alessandro Nivola, The Eye, Laurel Canyon). Diagnosed with a terminal illness, Nat shanghais his reluctant son into driving him cross-country for experimental medical treatment. Low on cash, they pull off increasingly ridiculous and embarrassing schemes along the way to reach their destination spending only $5 a day. Boasting a star-packed cast that includes Sharon Stone, Amanda Peet and Dean Cain, $5 A DAY is an irresistibly fresh and charming comedy about letting go of the past and choosing your own road.

shows.title: 'Neath Brooklyn Bridge
shows.overview: Muggs and the East Side Kids come to the rescue of a wrongly-accused girl, who is discovered in the home of a man murdered by a mystery assailant.

shows.title: 'Twas the Night
shows.overview: When Santa Claus is accidentally knocked out on Christmas Eve, Danny and his con-artist uncle Nick take it upon themselves to deliver the gifts. But while Danny is driving the sled, Nick steals from the neighbors. Can Danny show Nick the error of his ways and save Christmas at the same time?

shows.title: 'Twas the Night Before Christmas
shows.overview: A Hallmark Channel original movie. Madison, a former actress trying to break into directing, tests her skills by taking on a Christmas Eve courtroom production in which the true authorship of the famous poem A Visit from St. Nick is debated.

shows.title: 'Twas the Text Before Christmas
shows.overview: An unexpected text message sent to the wrong number sets into motion a Christmas tradition with a new family over three separate years.

shows.title: (500) Days of Summer
shows.overview: In this anti- romantic comedy about love and fate, a young greeting card writer (Joseph Gordon-Levitt) is hopelessly, helplessly searching for the girl of his dreams...and his new co-worker, Summer Finn (Zooey Deschanel), may just be "the one." But the 500 days of their offbeat relationship reveal that the road to happiness can be unpredictable, uncontrollable and unbelievable.
